{% extends "base.prompt.njk" %}

{% block section_specific %}

Generate key insights and future outlook for the disease below.
This is the final and most important section of a professional
pharma report — it synthesises everything established across
all previous sections into strategic conclusions.

DISEASE: {{ disease.name }}
{% if disease.description %}
DESCRIPTION: {{ disease.description }}
{% endif %}

{% if context %}
─────────────────────────────────────
FULL REPORT CONTEXT:
{{ context }}
─────────────────────────────────────
This context summarises all previous sections of the report.
Your insights must be grounded in and consistent with this
context. Do not introduce facts that contradict it.
Synthesise across sections — do not summarise one section alone.
{% endif %}

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
WHAT TO GENERATE
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

STRUCTURED FIELDS
Each array item should be a concise, punchy, standalone string.

{% for field in section.structured_fields %}
"{{ field.name }}"
  Type       : {{ field.type }}
  Task       : {{ field.description }}
  {% if field.example %}
  Example    : {{ field.example | dump }}
  {% endif %}
  ⚠ Required — minimum {{ section.validation.min_array_length[field.name] }} items

{% endfor %}

NARRATIVE FIELDS

{% for field in section.freetext_fields %}
"{{ field.name }}"
  Task       : {{ field.description }}
  Word limit : {{ field.min_words }}–{{ field.max_words }} words
  ⚠ Required
{% endfor %}

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
GUIDELINES
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Tone: {{ section.prompt_hints.tone }}

Avoid:
{% for item in section.prompt_hints.avoid %}
  - {{ item }}
{% endfor %}

Prefer:
{% for item in section.prompt_hints.prefer %}
  - {{ item }}
{% endfor %}

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
OUTPUT FORMAT
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Return a single valid JSON object.
No backticks. No explanation. No extra keys.
Start your response with { and end with }

{% endblock %}